                        "displayName": "Steve Hollis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The 'Errors' decorator (Zend_Form_Decorator_Errors) is designed for use with form elements whilst the 'FormErrors' (Zend_Form_Decorator_FormErrors) decorator is designed for use with whole forms.\r\n\r\nYou can use one or other or both, but the right decorator must be applied to the right object type.\r\n\r\nSee docs: http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/manual\/en\/zend.form.standardDecorators.html#zend.form.standardDecorators.errors",
